{"tid":2178971,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"涉1月19日藏噴漆　前學民錢詩文禁足旺角及宵禁","createTime":"2020-08-28T19:16:24.000Z","updateTime":"2020-08-28T20:09:07.000Z","uid":240362,"like":1,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"ed2a520c8df45a76062b4799aa9bd4e6d2d0c8dc","tid":2178971,"uid":240362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-28T19:16:24.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20200829/SMTXZIHIABD6HCXYZVW2UQ5D4U/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200829%2FSMTXZIHIABD6HCXYZVW2UQ5D4U%2F&d=7GjM3WQHKJNqnWTuO28XyMF7E3yEolOTrLLafiBe6Y0%3D&h=d2e57edc\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200829%2FSMTXZIHIABD6HCXYZVW2UQ5D4U%2F&h=31fd8fee\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20200829/SMTXZIHIABD6HCXYZVW2UQ5D4U/</a><br />\n<br />\n民間集會團隊於今年1月19日在中環遮打花園舉行「天下制裁」集會，集會最終遭警方腰斬，並演變成警民衝突，入夜後旺角等地均有示威。其間前學民思潮成員錢詩文在旺角被截查，搜出一罐噴漆，事隔半年，被控一項管有物品意圖摧毀財產罪。此外，一名女會計師被指於今年6月12日在旺角街頭被搜出一支雷射筆，被控在公眾地方管有攻擊性武器罪。兩案昨日於西九龍法院提堂，主任裁判官羅德泉批准兩被告保釋，但下令兩人禁足旺角及宵禁。"},{"pid":"a19d0c0d86034d015d83e793eac5b2f0bc5e2e90","tid":2178971,"uid":285559,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-28T19:39:39.000Z","msg":"噴漆咁大殺傷力 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5e00bcecfb5d6fab63f8ee797dfdeca8df1b95aa","tid":2178971,"uid":21545,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-28T19:44:34.000Z","msg":"去高院上訴"},{"pid":"70bd01e419c5ce82267d045c81d11df4364e50e8","tid":2178971,"uid":325346,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-28T19:48:55.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 死黑警"},{"pid":"12c2a7c709973c3550dfba629b2f306fb8239